I"5<h2 id="prospective-graduate-students">Prospective Graduate Students</h2>

<p>Admissions for graduate students in our department are conducted independent of funding and centrally for the Robotics Institute. Please apply directly to the institute and contact me once you have been admitted (Usually in February).</p>

<h2 id="current-carnegie-mellon-students">Current Carnegie Mellon Students</h2>

<p>Please send Sebastian an <a href="mailto:basti@andrew.cmu.edu">email</a> if you are interested in working with the lab.</p>

<h2 id="staffpostdoc-positions">Staff/Postdoc Positions</h2>

<p>If you are interested in a research staff or postdoc position in our areas of research please send Sebastian an <a href="mailto:basti@andrew.cmu.edu">email</a> with your resume/CV and a description of your particular skills.</p>
